DailyCouponExpirationTask - Class in utils
This class is for creating the DailyCouponExpirationTask thread, that is created in order to check - at startup of the system, and then every 24 hours after it's last check - all of the coupons that are expired and deleting them from the system.
DailyCouponExpirationTask() - Constructor for class utils.DailyCouponExpirationTask
constructs the DailyCouponExpirationTask and creating a new couponDBDAO object for the thread's use.
